    "These models will aid in constructing systematic frameworks for swift disease diagnosis and suggesting novel antibiotics with unique mechanisms of action.",
    "For antibiotic discovery, this means going beyond hit generation proofs-of-concept as well as considering more secondary properties besides toxicity and integrating AI in the later stages of drug development.",
